### Get Active Subscription (as Member)
GET https://localhost:7259/api/members/active-subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{member_token}}

### Get Active Subscription (as Admin for self)
GET https://localhost:7259/api/members/active-subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get Active Subscription (as Admin for specific member)
GET https://localhost:7259/api/members/active-subscription?memberId=01948372-5a3d-7b2e-a1c4-83920174be62
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get Active Subscription (Unauthorized - Member requesting for other)
GET https://localhost:7259/api/members/active-subscription?memberId=01948372-5a3d-7b2e-a1c4-83920174be62
Authorization: Bearer {{member_token}}